data.text: @LeeFortin Wish ya the best of luck this week! We hope to finish wed and Thursday! 460 of #durum left #nobreakdowns 🤞
@farmercharmer1 Ya we had quite a swath of hail delayed a lot of crop then we got caught in this weather. Corn was expected to be late also. If this week holds true we should be able to wrap it up.
